<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Архив 2026</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Source+Code+Pro:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-body: #f0f4f8;
            --bg-card: #ffffff;
            --text-primary: #2d3748;
            --text-secondary: #718096;
            --accent-color: #4c51bf;
            --accent-light: #ebf4ff;
            --success-color: #38a169;
            --danger-color: #e53e3e;
            --warning-color: #dd6b20;
            --code-bg: #f7fafc;
            --border-color: #e2e8f0;
            --shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.025);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-body);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }

        .date-label {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent-light);
            color: var(--accent-color);
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .date-label.red {
            background: rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.1);
            color: var(--danger-color);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .stat-item { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .stat-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }
        .progress-bg {
            background: #edf2f7;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-color), #667eea);
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        blockquote {
            background: var(--bg-body);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);
            padding: 20px 30px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .math-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
        }
        .math-box {
            background: var(--bg-body);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            min-width: 60px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .math-val {
            display: block;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        .math-char {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        pre {
            background: var(--code-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #4a5568;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .highlight { color: var(--accent-color); font-weight: 600; }
        .success-text { color: var(--success-color); font-weight: 700; }
        
        .study-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .stat-box {
            background: var(--bg-body);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .stat-value {
            display: block;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .score-highlight {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--success-color);
        }

        .tree-container {
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
            background: var(--code-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .tree-title {
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px dashed var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .tree-node { margin-left: 20px; position: relative; }
        .tree-node::before {
            content: "│";
            position: absolute;
            left: -12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .tree-branch {
            margin: 4px 0;
            padding-left: 15px;
            border-left: 2px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .condition {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 700;
            background: var(--accent-light);
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .decision {
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .decision.approved { background: rgba(56, 161, 105, 0.15); color: var(--success-color); }
        .decision.denied { background: rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.15); color: var(--danger-color); }
        .decision.warning { background: rgba(221, 107, 32, 0.15); color: var(--warning-color); }
        .probability {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-left: 8px;
        }
        .branch-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-right: 6px;
        }
        .branch-yes { background: rgba(56, 161, 105, 0.2); color: var(--success-color); }
        .branch-no { background: rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.2); color: var(--danger-color); }
        
        .accuracy-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-light), #f7fafc);
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .accuracy-value {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        .accuracy-label {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .diagnostic-block {
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
            background: var(--code-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #4a5568;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .diagnostic-header {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 12px 0 8px;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            border-bottom: 2px dashed var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .epoch-log {
            margin: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 10px;
            border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-light);
        }
        .epoch-line {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 3px 0;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .epoch-num { color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .epoch-mse { 
            font-weight: 700; 
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
        }
        .completion-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: rgba(56, 161, 105, 0.15);
            color: var(--success-color);
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .results-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .result-box {
            background: var(--bg-body);
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .result-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .result-value {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
        }
        .result-value.good { color: var(--success-color); }
        .result-value.warn { color: var(--warning-color); }
        
        .prediction-list {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 2px dashed var(--border-color);
        }
        .prediction-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            margin: 6px 0;
            background: var(--bg-body);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .prediction-fact { color: var(--success-color); font-weight: 700; }
        .prediction-pred { color: var(--accent-color); font-weight: 700; }
        .prediction-sep { color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0 6px; }
        
        .comparison-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .comparison-table th {
            background: var(--accent-light);
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .comparison-table td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .comparison-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
        .comparison-table tr:hover { background: var(--bg-body); }
        .mse-val { font-weight: 700; text-align: right; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace; }
        .mse-val.better { color: var(--success-color); }
        .mse-val.worse { color: var(--danger-color); }
        
        .model-insight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-light), #f7fafc);
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .model-insight strong { color: var(--accent-color); }
        .insight-warning { color: var(--warning-color); font-weight: 600; }

        .flowchart-container {
            background: var(--bg-body);
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        
        .flowchart-image {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .algorithm-description {
            background: var(--accent-light);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .algorithm-description h3 {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .algorithm-description ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        
        .algorithm-description li {
            margin: 8px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .diagram-frame {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        
        .diagram-frame img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .db-description {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-light), #f0f9ff);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .db-description h3 {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .db-description ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        
        .db-description li {
            margin: 8px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .patient-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .patient-stat-box {
            background: var(--bg-body);
            padding: 15px 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .patient-stat-value {
            display: block;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        .patient-stat-value.total { color: var(--accent-color); }
        .patient-stat-value.emergency { color: var(--danger-color); }
        .patient-stat-value.planned { color: var(--success-color); }
        .patient-stat-value.self { color: var(--warning-color); }
        .patient-stat-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-top: 4px;
            display: block;
        }

        .comparison-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        
        .comparison-card table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            min-width: 500px;
        }
        
        .comparison-card th {
            background: var(--accent-light);
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
        }
        
        .comparison-card td {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        
        .comparison-card tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .comparison-card tr:hover {
            background: var(--bg-body);
        }
        
        .comparison-card td:first-child {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background: var(--bg-body);
        }
        
        .stars {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-align: center;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .stars.best { color: var(--success-color); }
        .stars.good { color: var(--accent-color); }
        .stars.avg { color: var(--warning-color); }
        .stars.poor { color: var(--danger-color); }
        
        .table-legend {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px dashed var(--border-color);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        
        .legend-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
        }
        
        .legend-stars {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .download-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: var(--success-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .download-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(56, 161, 105, 0.3);
        }

        details {
            background: var(--bg-body);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        summary {
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            outline: none;
        }
        summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
        summary::before {
            content: "▶ ";
            display: inline-block;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        details[open] summary::before {
            transform: rotate(90deg);
        }

        /* Стили для блока схем индексных файлов */
        .db-schema-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .db-schema-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .db-schema-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .db-schema-card-header {
            padding: 15px 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .db-schema-card-header.doctor {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ebf5fb, #d4e6f1);
            color: #2874a6;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #3498db;
        }

        .db-schema-card-header.nurse {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f8f5, #d1f2eb);
            color: #1e8449;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2ecc71;
        }

        .db-schema-card-header.operation {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fde8e8, #f5b7b1);
            color: #922b21;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #e74c3c;
        }

        .db-schema-card-header.secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef9e7, #f9e79f);
            color: #7d6608;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #f1c40f;
        }

        .db-schema-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .db-schema-full {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .db-schema-full img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .entity-list {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .entity-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .entity-badge.doctor {
            background: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
            color: #2874a6;
            border: 2px solid rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3);
        }

        .entity-badge.nurse {
            background: rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.1);
            color: #1e8449;
            border: 2px solid rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.3);
        }

        .entity-badge.operation {
            background: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.1);
            color: #922b21;
            border: 2px solid rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);
        }

        .section-divider {
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-color), transparent);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .patient-stats {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
            .study-stats {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .comparison-card table {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
            .comparison-card th,
            .comparison-card td {
                padding: 8px 10px;
            }
            .db-schema-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>DevLog 2026</h1>
            <p>Цифровой архив и наблюдения</p>
        </header>

        <!-- 🔹 НОВЫЙ БЛОК: 11 апреля 2026 - Схемы индексных файлов -->
        <article class="card">
            <span class="date-label red">11 апреля 2026</span>
            <h2>🗄️ Стоматологическое отделение: Схемы индексных файлов</h2>
            <p>Полная реализация иерархических моделей и индексных структур для трёх сущностей стоматологического отделения:</p>

            <!-- Сущности -->
            <div class="entity-list">
                <div class="entity-badge doctor">👨‍️ Врач</div>
                <div class="entity-badge nurse">👩‍⚕️ Медсестра</div>
                <div class="entity-badge operation">⚕️ Операция</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Сводная схема иерархии -->
